95
00:08:27,756 --> 00:08:28,756
I'm dead.

96
00:08:30,175 --> 00:08:31,592
You're totally broke?

97
00:08:32,302 --> 00:08:33,761
We'll be okay, doll.

98
00:08:33,929 --> 00:08:35,179
Won't we?

99
00:08:36,181 --> 00:08:39,475
Sure we will. We'll pull through. You'll see.

100
00:08:39,809 --> 00:08:41,727
You fat, worthless fool.

101
00:08:41,853 --> 00:08:43,312
Belle, wait.

102
00:08:48,068 --> 00:08:51,153
Well, what other tricks do you know?

103
