119
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:41,370
Come here, to Chicago.

120
00:09:41,871 --> 00:09:43,455
Into the lion's den?

121
00:09:43,540 --> 00:09:46,166
Yes. But before you do that,

122
00:09:46,710 --> 00:09:48,627
I want you to think hard
about who in this town

123
00:09:48,712 --> 00:09:50,337
