124
00:10:12,652 --> 00:10:13,777
Commodore, sir.

125
00:10:13,862 --> 00:10:15,029
Jesus.

126
00:10:17,407 --> 00:10:18,490
What is it?

127
00:10:18,908 --> 00:10:20,326
Your visitor, he's here.

128
00:10:21,036 --> 00:10:22,036
Oh.

129
00:10:22,954 --> 00:10:24,079
Good.

130
00:10:25,874 --> 00:10:27,249
Show him in.

131
00:10:43,308 --> 00:10:44,933
There's the boy.

132
00:10:46,770 --> 00:10:48,479
May I get you something, sir?

133
00:10:49,481 --> 00:10:50,731
No, I'm fine. Thank you.

134
00:10:50,815 --> 00:10:52,441
Nonsense. Get him a drink.

135
00:10:54,652 --> 00:10:56,653
No, no, you go on. I'll do it.

136
00:11:02,744 --> 00:11:04,453
Leave that there, for Christ's sake.

137
00:11:08,416 --> 00:11:09,500
So...

138
00:11:11,378 --> 00:11:12,669
Look at you.

139
00:11:14,047 --> 00:11:15,464
A proper gentleman.

140
00:11:17,425 --> 00:11:19,093
My mother raised me well.

141
00:11:20,804 --> 00:11:21,804
Biscuit?

142
00:11:31,314 --> 00:11:33,524
Yeah, he passed last night.

143
00:11:34,818 --> 00:11:38,654
